43:["$","p",null,{"children":"DNS（域名系统）将域名解析为 IP 地址，是互联网的基础设施之一。DNS 的安全威胁包括："}]
44:["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"DNS 劫持"}],"：修改 DNS 解析结果，将用户导向恶意网站"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"DNS 缓存投毒"}],"：向 DNS 缓存服务器注入伪造的记录"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"DNS 隧道"}],"：利用 DNS 查询/响应来建立隐蔽的数据传输通道"]}],"\n"]}]
46:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"防护措施"}],"：部署 DNSSEC（DNS 安全扩展）对 DNS 响应进行签名验证；使用 DoH（DNS over HTTPS）或 DoT（DNS over TLS）加密 DNS 查询；定期检查和监控 DNS 解析结果。"]}]
47:["$","h3",null,{"id":"http-明文传输风险","children":["HTTP 明文传输风险",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#http-明文传输风险","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}]
48:["$","p",null,{"children":"HTTP 协议以明文传输数据，攻击者可以通过网络嗅探轻松截获用户的敏感信息，包括登录凭证、Cookie 和个人数据。这也是为什么全站 HTTPS 已成为行业标准的原因。"}]
4a:["$","h2",null,{"id":"各层防护措施总览","children":["各层防护措施总览",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#各层防护措施总览","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}]
4b:["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"层次"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"主要威胁"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"关键防护措施"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"链路层"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"ARP 欺骗、MAC 泛洪"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"静态 ARP 绑定、端口安全、802.1X"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"网络层"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"IP 欺骗、ICMP 攻击"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"反向路径过滤、ACL、ICMP 速率限制"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"传输层"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"SYN Flood、会话劫持"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"SYN Cookies、加密传输、IDS/IPS"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"应用层"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"DNS 劫持、HTTP 明文"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"DNSSEC、HTTPS、WAF、安全编码"}]]}]]}]]}]
4c:["$","h2",null,{"id":"总结","children":["总结",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#总结","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}]
4d:["$","p",null,{"children":"TCP/IP 协议栈的安全性是网络安全的基石。从链路层的 ARP 欺骗到应用层的 DNS 劫持，每一层都存在特定的安全隐患。理解这些威胁的原理和攻击方式，是制定有效防御策略的前提。在实际的安全建设中，应当采用纵深防御的思路，在协议栈的每一层部署相应的安全措施：链路层的端口安全和 ARP 防护、网络层的访问控制和反欺骗过滤、传输层的 SYN Cookies 和加密传输、应用层的 WAF 和安全编码。同时，持续的安全监控和日志审计也是不可或缺的环节，它们能帮助我们及时发现和响应安全事件。只有从底层协议到上层应用的全面防护，才能构建起真正可靠的网络安全体系。"}]
4e:I[980,["382","static/chunks/382-8cd0914aab3203e0.js","153","static/chunks/153-17fe24b6f7f024ce.js","479","static/chunks/app/(site)/posts/%5Bslug%5D/page-88080a839ad6aac3.js"],"CopyButton"]
30:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 使用 arpspoof 实施 ARP 欺骗（仅限授权测试环境）\n\n# 开启 IP 转发，确保流量可以继续传输\necho 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward\n\n# 欺骗目标主机（192.168.1.100），使其认为攻击者是网关（192.168.1.1）\nsudo arpspoof -i eth0 -t 192.168.1.100 192.168.1.1\n\n# 同时欺骗网关，使其认为攻击者是目标主机\nsudo arpspoof -i eth0 -t 192.168.1.1 192.168.1.100\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 使用 arpspoof 实施 ARP 欺骗（仅限授权测试环境）\n\n# 开启 IP 转发，确保流量可以继续传输\necho 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward\n\n# 欺骗目标主机（192.168.1.100），使其认为攻击者是网关（192.168.1.1）\nsudo arpspoof -i eth0 -t 192.168.1.100 192.168.1.1\n\n# 同时欺骗网关，使其认为攻击者是目标主机\nsudo arpspoof -i eth0 -t 192.168.1.1 192.168.1.100\n"}]}]]}]
31:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 在 Linux 上绑定静态 ARP 表项，防止 ARP 欺骗\nsudo arp -s 192.168.1.1 aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff\n\n# 使用 arpwatch 监控 ARP 表变化\nsudo apt install arpwatch\nsudo arpwatch -i eth0\n\n# 查看当前 ARP 缓存\narp -a\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 在 Linux 上绑定静态 ARP 表项，防止 ARP 欺骗\nsudo arp -s 192.168.1.1 aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff\n\n# 使用 arpwatch 监控 ARP 表变化\nsudo apt install arpwatch\nsudo arpwatch -i eth0\n\n# 查看当前 ARP 缓存\narp -a\n"}]}]]}]
32:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 使用 macof 工具演示 MAC 泛洪（仅限授权测试环境）\nsudo macof -i eth0 -n 100000\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 使用 macof 工具演示 MAC 泛洪（仅限授权测试环境）\nsudo macof -i eth0 -n 100000\n"}]}]]}]
33:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 使用 hping3 发送伪造源 IP 的数据包（仅限授权测试环境）\n\n# 伪造源 IP 发送 SYN 包\nsudo hping3 -S -a 10.0.0.50 -p 80 192.168.1.100\n\n# 使用随机源 IP 发送大量包\nsudo hping3 --rand-source -S -p 80 --flood 192.168.1.100\n\n# 发送指定大小的 ICMP 包进行探测\nsudo hping3 -1 -d 64 192.168.1.100\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 使用 hping3 发送伪造源 IP 的数据包（仅限授权测试环境）\n\n# 伪造源 IP 发送 SYN 包\nsudo hping3 -S -a 10.0.0.50 -p 80 192.168.1.100\n\n# 使用随机源 IP 发送大量包\nsudo hping3 --rand-source -S -p 80 --flood 192.168.1.100\n\n# 发送指定大小的 ICMP 包进行探测\nsudo hping3 -1 -d 64 192.168.1.100\n"}]}]]}]
34:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 配置 iptables 进行反欺骗过滤（RFC 2827 / BCP 38）\n# 丢弃声称来自内网但从外网接口进入的数据包\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -i eth0 -s 192.168.1.0/24 -j DROP\n\n# 启用反向路径过滤（Reverse Path Filtering）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter=1\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.default.rp_filter=1\n\n# 写入配置文件使其永久生效\necho \"net.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter = 1\" >> /etc/sysctl.conf\nsudo sysctl -p\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 配置 iptables 进行反欺骗过滤（RFC 2827 / BCP 38）\n# 丢弃声称来自内网但从外网接口进入的数据包\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -i eth0 -s 192.168.1.0/24 -j DROP\n\n# 启用反向路径过滤（Reverse Path Filtering）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter=1\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.default.rp_filter=1\n\n# 写入配置文件使其永久生效\necho \"net.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter = 1\" >> /etc/sysctl.conf\nsudo sysctl -p\n"}]}]]}]
35:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 防御 ICMP 相关攻击\n\n# 禁止 ICMP 重定向（防止路由篡改）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects=0\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.send_redirects=0\n\n# 限制 ICMP 请求速率（防止 Ping Flood）\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type echo-request \\\n  -m limit --limit 1/s --limit-burst 4 -j ACCEPT\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type echo-request -j DROP\n\n# 禁用广播地址响应（防止 Smurf 攻击）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 防御 ICMP 相关攻击\n\n# 禁止 ICMP 重定向（防止路由篡改）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects=0\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.send_redirects=0\n\n# 限制 ICMP 请求速率（防止 Ping Flood）\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type echo-request \\\n  -m limit --limit 1/s --limit-burst 4 -j ACCEPT\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type echo-request -j DROP\n\n# 禁用广播地址响应（防止 Smurf 攻击）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1\n"}]}]]}]
3a:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# SYN Flood 防护措施\n\n# 启用 SYN Cookies — 最有效的 SYN Flood 防御手段\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1\n\n# 减小 SYN_RECV 状态的超时时间\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries=2\n\n# 增大半连接队列长度\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog=4096\n\n# 使用 iptables 限制 SYN 包速率\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn \\\n  -m limit --limit 50/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -j DROP\n\n# 查看当前半连接数量\nnetstat -an | grep SYN_RECV | wc -l\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# SYN Flood 防护措施\n\n# 启用 SYN Cookies — 最有效的 SYN Flood 防御手段\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1\n\n# 减小 SYN_RECV 状态的超时时间\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries=2\n\n# 增大半连接队列长度\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog=4096\n\n# 使用 iptables 限制 SYN 包速率\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn \\\n  -m limit --limit 50/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT\nsudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -j DROP\n\n# 查看当前半连接数量\nnetstat -an | grep SYN_RECV | wc -l\n"}]}]]}]
3f:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 启用 TCP 时间戳（增加序列号预测难度）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_timestamps=1\n\n# 配置更随机的初始序列号\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_window_scaling=1\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 启用 TCP 时间戳（增加序列号预测难度）\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_timestamps=1\n\n# 配置更随机的初始序列号\nsudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_window_scaling=1\n"}]}]]}]
45:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 使用 dig 检查 DNS 解析是否被篡改\ndig @8.8.8.8 example.com A +short\ndig @1.1.1.1 example.com A +short\n\n# 检查 DNSSEC 签名验证\ndig example.com +dnssec +short\n\n# 查看完整的 DNS 解析链\ndig example.com +trace\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 使用 dig 检查 DNS 解析是否被篡改\ndig @8.8.8.8 example.com A +short\ndig @1.1.1.1 example.com A +short\n\n# 检查 DNSSEC 签名验证\ndig example.com +dnssec +short\n\n# 查看完整的 DNS 解析链\ndig example.com +trace\n"}]}]]}]
49:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L4e",null,{"text":"# 使用 tshark 演示 HTTP 明文传输的风险\n# 捕获 HTTP 请求中的密码字段（仅限授权测试环境）\nsudo tshark -i eth0 -Y \"http.request.method == POST\" \\\n  -T fields -e http.host -e http.request.uri -e http.file_data\n\n# 测试目标网站是否支持 HTTPS\ncurl -I https://example.com\nopenssl s_client -connect example.com:443 -brief\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-bash","children":"# 使用 tshark 演示 HTTP 明文传输的风险\n# 捕获 HTTP 请求中的密码字段（仅限授权测试环境）\nsudo tshark -i eth0 -Y \"http.request.method == POST\" \\\n  -T fields -e http.host -e http.request.uri -e http.file_data\n\n# 测试目标网站是否支持 HTTPS\ncurl -I https://example.com\nopenssl s_client -connect example.com:443 -brief\n"}]}]]}]
